BahrainSweet

Ingredients
A cup of sugar
8 cups water
Saffron Brush
1/2 cup rose water
3/4 cup starch
3 tbsp gelatin, dissolved in a quarter cup warm water
3/4 cup vegetable oil
2 cups different nuts, crushe

Steps

Place the whole sugar and stir with a wooden spoon over low heat until boiling.
Dissolve the starch in a glass of water and add the rest of the water to the sugar with continuous stirring.
Add the oil, rose water, saffron and halo to the mixture and continue stirring.
Now add starch mixture and gelatin mixture and continue stirring until boiling.
